flowchart LR
    A[Channel order] --> B[Channel adapter ingest]
    B --> C[Canonical Order created]
    C --> D[Validation + auto-rules]
    D --> E[Ready_to_ship]
    E --> F[Rate quote + carrier select]
    F --> G[Two-phase wallet reserve]
    G --> H[Carrier book]
    H --> I[AWB + label + manifest]
    I --> J[Pickup_Pending]
    J --> K[Picked_Up]
    K --> L[In_Transit]
    L --> M[Out_For_Delivery]
    M --> N[Delivered]
    N --> O[Buyer notified + COD remittance flow]
    M --> P[NDR]
    P --> Q[Reattempt or RTO]
    Q --> N
    Q --> R[RTO_Initiated]
    R --> S[RTO_Delivered]
